{"tid":2252990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"處理車禍後離場 騎警意外遭同袍撼低","createTime":"2020-10-22T00:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T01:27:40.000Z","uid":230530,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5198f5b9c31dd458efb0789a08afe5044ef78680","tid":2252990,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"將軍澳寶寧路與坑口道交界迴旋處，凌晨5時許，警方交通部一輛電單車與一輛私家車款的警車，在迴旋處發生輕微碰撞，駕駛電單車的交通警員翻車墮地擦傷，電單車左邊車身損毀，警方私家車則車頭泵把受損，救護員趕至現場，將受傷警員送院治理，車禍原因有待調查。兩警車上的警員，於事發前在距現場約200米外，處理完一宗送外賣電單車的交通意外，兩車離開後不久即告相撞。"},{"pid":"f8f3757e091f40c1612fb953a31f9f5c24a915c3","tid":2252990,"uid":36995,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPiJyDU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPiJyDU.gif&h=577e46db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60ce6f9b9a8b430500b0d043328d37d02125f60c","tid":2252990,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:49:07.000Z","msg":"啲黑警又出來柒了"},{"pid":"1ad14563b1a76a84ada94f4746be5fd58d4d426a","tid":2252990,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648079e11a345e8649df5d1725bdceafd8b698f6","tid":2252990,"uid":33711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2adbf5c0ce52954616ede689532c79a3792477","tid":2252990,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T00:55:11.000Z","msg":"係美國一早開左槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b036041